{"tid":1334223,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"迪卡儂頭盔存貨推介","createTime":"2019-07-20T04:30:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T09:40:52.000Z","uid":273269,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"f9e73539b1827388a4e168b1712f28fd7e2c5541","tid":1334223,"uid":273269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T04:30:39.000Z","msg":"迪卡儂旺角現場暫時得返三款頭盔，有99$（單車部）丶169$（單車部）丶189$（攀石部）三款。其實三款既內材質都係泡綿，舒適度都係一樣。另外外材質都係ABS樹脂。<br />\n所以其實99$款已經夠用，只係戴完會變薯仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果你地想買169＄款既，我會建議你行去攀石部買189$，無論外型固定度都比較好，仲可以裝頭燈添<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n至於有手足話，頭盔戴落去唔舒服，感覺瀉唔到好多力，其實只要外層夠硬就得。改裝好容易，只要你喺頭盔裏面加多層海綿布（土炮可以百潔布嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />），咁舒適度同避震就會增強，隨你喜歡去改<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n提提大家，試頭盔嘅時候，後面係會有個圓形轉轉去調校鬆緊，符合個人大細㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n手足加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nh7W3Mk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnh7W3Mk.png&h=2b3919f6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vxA9EjJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvxA9EjJ.png&h=2b1b7c21&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6iPixEL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6iPixEL.png&h=ea1ac545&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5dmQoMu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5dmQoMu.png&h=2d506d8c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a065639e9525ef35be38e9e17d22d55c7caa2f01","tid":1334223,"uid":55598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T04:31:37.000Z","msg":"仲有冇背囊？"},{"pid":"029ec6271fa5bc26378be9607884e72f7ff1a6ed","tid":1334223,"uid":273269,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a065639e9525ef35be38e9e17d22d55c7caa2f01"